attB_1057x453.jpg','<p>T</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(111,26,1,'King','5145-King_1057x453.jpg','<p>King</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(112,26,1,'California King','8426-Cal-King_1057x453.jpg','<p>Cal King</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(113,103,2,'Corona 8\" ','6814-Corona_1500x1000.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Corona Is one of our most popular value priced mattress lines. &nbsp;100% USA Made and featuring a 8&quot; profile, puffy quilted top and Bonnell Coil Spring Unit made in the USA.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Great for guest rooms, students, kids and Airbnb</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(114,103,2,'Carmel Pillow Top ','7471-Carmel_1057x453.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Nice step up to the Corona, the Carmel features&nbsp;a 9 1/2&quot; profile, quilted pillow top and Bonnell Coil Spring Unit made in the USA. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Nice medium feel and comfort&nbsp;pillow top feature ads a nice bonus to this great priced mattress.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Great for guest rooms, students, kids and Airbnb and anyone in need of a well priced quality mattress.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(115,103,2,'Value Pillow Top 10\"','1382-Value-Comfort-Pillow-Top-Mattress_1057x453.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">What a great value we have for you in the this 10&quot; Plush&nbsp;Pillow Top Mattress. Appx 10&quot; thick nice white comfy top you won&#39;t find in any other mattress set for this price.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The Value Comfort Pillow Top&nbsp;is one of the most popular mattresses we have offering a great price for a good quality mattress. Available in several sizes in stock for same day delivery.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(117,103,2,'St. Maarten Pillow Top 12\"','6353-St.-Maarten-Corner_1057x453a.jpg','<p>Twin Mattress</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(118,103,2,'Biotic Pillow Top 12\"','3525-Biotic Mattress Pillow Top_230x175.jpg','<p>CC</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(123,103,2,'Napa','4059-Napa Set1_PS_1057x453.jpg','<p>cc</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(124,105,2,'Chenille Firm Mattress','5321-Chenille-Firm-Mattress-Fulla_1057x453.jpg','<p>Chenille</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(125,105,2,'Crystal Medium Firm ','804-Crystal Mattress Med FirmB_1057x453.jpg','<p>Crystal Med Firm</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(126,104,2,'Carmel Pillow Top ','465-Carmel Mattress View_1057x453.jpg','<p>Carmel Pillow Top</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(127,104,2,'Value Comfort Pillow Top','8268-Value-Comfort-Pillow-Top-Mattress_1057x453.jpg','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The Value Comfort is a great value pillow top mattress. &nbsp;It has a Leggett &amp; Platt 396 Bonnell Coil system and a nice soft cotton cover for a nice medium feel. &nbsp;These mattresses are also warrantied for 12 years</span></p>\r\n','active',0,''),(130,104,2,'St. Maarten Euro Pillow Top ','7944-St. Maarten Corner_230x175a.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The St. Maarten&nbsp;has been a staple Pillow Top Mattress of Mattress Store San Diego for years! It&#39;s a great value because of it&#39;s thick profile so you have lots of comfy foam over the springs.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Built to last, the St. Maarten&nbsp;Mattress collection is perfect for any room in the house a better bed than youll find in many stores at a fraction of the price.</span></p>\r\n','active',0,''),(131,104,2,'Biotic Pillow Top','7162-Biotic_1030x700.jpg','<p>Biotic Pillow Top</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(133,104,2,'Napa Pillow Top','2216-Napa Mattress Set_1030x700.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The Napa Pillow Top Mattress collection features a nice medium feel with an upgraded verticoil spring system that helps prevent motion transfer compared to a regular Bonnell Coil. &nbsp; Foam encased edge supports add to the sleeping surface as well as add stability and structure.</span></p>\r\n','active',0,''),(134,104,2,'Soft Sleep','9804-Soft Sleep Mattress Corner_1030x700.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Great soft feel with an indivually wrap coil system, encased foam edge supports and a soft white stretch knit cotton cover.</span></p>\r\n','active',0,''),(135,104,2,'Miralux Plush','8332-Miralux Mattress Plush_Crop_1030x700.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">If you enjoy a soft comfort, the Sleep Inc by Corsicana Miralux Euro Pillow Top is one of the best values found on our site. The Verticoil system, comfort layers, and quilt all contain nice features typically reserved for mattresses much higher in price. With a Comfort Scale rating of 7, this is a good choice for side sleepers or back sleepers who enjoy a soft, enveloping initial feel with solid underlying support. Features also a Tencel Fiber soft cover that helps keep you cooler and full foam encased edge support to add to the sleep surface.</span></p>\r\n','active',0,''),(136,104,2,'Bridgeton ','4339-Bridgeton Pillow Top Mattress_ Crop.jpg','<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The Bridgeton Pillow Top Mattress gives you a comfortable feel like the Miralux but with a slightly firmer feel. Over 14&quot; or rich, high quality comfort foams in an inviting pillow top that is comfortable and very supportive. The Verticoil system, comfort layers, and quilt all contain nice features typically reserved for mattresses much higher in price. This is a good choice for side sleepers or back sleepers who enjoy a soft initial feel with solid underlying support. Features also a TruCool soft cover that helps keep you cooler and full foam encased edge support to add to the sleep surface. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://Yelp.com/biz/mattress-store-san-diego-chula-vista-13\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">See my 200+ 5-Star Reviews on Yelp! </span></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(138,106,2,'Crystal ','7236-Crystal Mattress_1030x700_Corner.jpg','<p>Our Crystal mattress collection has a unique firm overall feel but with an initial plush top. &nbsp; Comfort and value comes from the Indivivual Wrap Coils and a nice soft Organic Cotton Quilted fabric that feels great and keeps you cooler. &nbsp;</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(139,0,0,'testsub_Category','3916-ways-to-say-good-morning.jpg','<p>sdfsfsd</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(140,139,1,'testcat','58-good-morning-starshine.jpg','<p>sdffdf</p>\r\n','active',0,''),(141,140,2,'testsub_sub','9068-good-morning-starshine.jpg','<p>testtest</p>\r\n','active',0,'');
